  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine whether fruit juice rich in polyphenols might increase exercise capacity and
      memory in healthy sedentary subjects.Both parameters might be improved because of the
      anti-oxidant effects of polyphenols.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
